                  <items count="4">
                    <item name="Description" type_name="gh_string" type_code="10">Define inflow boundary conditions from a manually entered vertical profile (z/zR, U/UR, k/UR^2) instead of the parametric ABL log-law. Writes fixedProfile inlet conditions for U, k and epsilon. epsilon is derived from the profile as epsilon(z) = Cmu^0.5 * k(z) * d(U)/dz.</item>
                    <item name="InstanceGuid" type_name="gh_guid" type_code="9">abf41370-7c99-4e47-a01c-76dee3b35dc9</item>
                    <item name="Name" type_name="gh_string" type_code="10">Manual Inflow Profile</item>
